214
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:04,432
Is that so?

215
00:08:04,435 --> 00:08:06,447
I had a good part in<i> Oklahoma.</i>

216
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:09,730
♪ I'm just a girl who can't say no. ♪

217
00:08:09,733 --> 00:08:10,752
